                                                            <h5 style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);"><strong>12. Restrictions on rates</strong></span></span></h5>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">12.1 Bookmaker company has the right not to accept bets from any person without giving any reason and reserves the right to close or temporarily block the accounts of individual Users without prior notice.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">12.2 Minimum and maximum size of bets for all sporting events is defined by the bookmaker office and is a subject to changes without prior written notice. In addition, Alivecasino reserves the right to impose special restrictions on the accounts of individual Users.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">12.3 Alivecasino does not recommend two or more Users to place bets from one IP-address (from the same computer or the same local area network) in order to avoid suspicion of collusion (cheating). In such cases it is necessary to reconcile the possibility of the game with Alivecasino by explaining the circumstances. Alivecasino has the right to block the account of such a User and ask them to send the documents verifying their registered identity.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">12.4 Winnings are paid only within the limits set with maximum limits of the company. If the User has made a bet and the winning exceeds the maximum, the company will not pay any amount of money exceeding the maximum limit.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">12.5 Results for sports statistics are published on the official website of Alivecasino within 3 days after the end of a sporting event.</span></span></p>
