                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">15.1 The User is responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any information related to their account, and shall take all measures to prevent the use of personal accounts by unauthorized persons. Any operations confirmed by the username and password of the account holder shall be valid and have legal force.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">15.2 If the User suspects that his username and password are known to a third person, at any time they have the right to send a request to Alivecasino to block the account temporarily for all circumstances to be made clear.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">15.3 To ensure the security of personal data of Users, Alivecasino communicates with Users via the e-mail indicated by the User during registration.</span></span></p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">15.4 The User is responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of any information related to their e- mail, and shall take all measures to prevent the use of e-mail address by third parties. Alivecasino is not responsible for any loss or damage resulting from the connection between the bookmaker office and the User using a registered e-mail address.</span></span></p>
