                                                        <div class="uc-content ">
                                                            <h5 style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);"><strong>17. Neutral field</strong></span></span></h5>
                                                            <p style="color:rgb(53, 53, 53);">&nbsp;</p>
                                                            <p style="color:rgba(49, 49, 49, 0.7);"><span style="font-family:Roboto;"><span style="color:rgb(64, 64, 64);">17.1 In cases when the match is transferred to a neutral field (NF) rates persist. They are refundable in cases when the match is transferred to the opponent’s field. In case of the play when the teams are from the same city and are transferred to another field, bets are valid and are not refundable. In international matches, the refund of bets is made only when the match transfers to the field of an opponent state.</span></span></p>
